                                                         "Congestion (0-10):", 
                                                         currentParams.networkCongestionLevel, 0, 10,
                                                         controlMouseX >= x + 10 && 
                                                         controlMouseX <= x + width - 10 &&
                                                         controlMouseY >= controlY && 
